FBIS3-43918 "drafr012_e_94005" FBIS-AFR-94-012 Document Type:Daily Report 19 Jan 1994 WEST AFRICA Nigeria Federal Government Approves Appointment of NEC Boss AB1901093594 Lagos Radio Nigeria in English 1800 GMT 17 Jan 94 AB1901093594 Lagos Radio Nigeria Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] The Federal Government has approved the appointment of Alhaji Mohamed Ali as the director general of the National Electoral Commission. Until this appointment, Alhaji Mohamed was director of personnel management and acting sole administrator of the commission. A statement in Abuja today said the appointment took effect from the 16th of last month.
